        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Blood and urine samples collected before and after each supplementation dose and 8 weeks after arrest of supplementation. Supplementation: daily intake of successive doses: increments of 200, 400, 800, and 1600 mg DHA (Decola, Maldegem, Belgium) for 2 weeks for each dose without interruption."
        }
